    <stitle>CAB: 2000, 4000, AND 8000 - DESCRIPTION - WINDSHIELD WASHER</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="IDcomponent" graphiccount="0">
        <title>WINDSHIELD WASHER</title>
        <para>The windshield washer consists of a reservoir mounted, motor driven, displacement type pump that delivers
            washer solution to the windshield through hoses and nozzles in the wiper arms. The pump motor may be
            integral with reservoir or detached.
        </para>
